---
/**
 * Solution section — who the founder is, why they can solve it
 */
---

<section id="solution" class="section solution">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="solution-inner">
      <div class="solution-text">
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: left;">
          Built OpenClaw. Now I'll Set It Up For You.
        </h2>
        <p class="solution-body">
          I'm the creator of OpenClaw. I've done hundreds of installations across
          every platform and configuration. Instead of spending hours troubleshooting
          alone, book a session with me and I'll get your AI agent running — guaranteed.
        </p>
        <ul class="solution-list">
          <li>Full installation and configuration</li>
          <li>WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord — any channel connected</li>
          <li>Custom SOUL.md personality setup</li>
          <li>Skills installed and tested</li>
          <li>You walk away with a working agent</li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="#pricing"
          class="btn btn-primary"
          onclick="trackEvent('cta_click', { tier: 'solution', location: 'solution' })"
        >
          See Pricing
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-visual">
        <div class="terminal-mock">
          <div class="terminal-header">
            <span class="dot red"></span>
            <span class="dot yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot green"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
            <p><span class="prompt">$</span> openclaw start</p>
            <p class="success">Agent is running on WhatsApp</p>
            <p class="success">SOUL.md loaded: friendly-assistant</p>
            <p class="success">3 skills active: calendar, weather, notes</p>
            <p class="muted">Ready to chat. Session complete.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .solution-body {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .solution-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .solution-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .solution-list li::before {
    content: '\2713';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .terminal-mock {
    background: #0d0d14;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot.red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot.green { background: #28c840; }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 20px;
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .terminal-body .prompt {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .terminal-body .success {
    color: var(--color-success);
  }

  .terminal-body .muted {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center !important;
    }
  }
</style>
